snippet.title: Shall we date?: Story Jar
snippet.description:
【Story Jar☺️✨💕】
Wand of Fortune, the hit game by Otomate, is finally getting an English release! You are a student attending the Mills Crea School of Magic in the Magic City of Latium, the control center for magic.
Make your way through the various trials and tribulations that await you, and seize the power of magic and love with your own hand!
The Prologue and Julius’ main story is out! Be sure to check them out! 

Play Now❗️❗️❗️
Story Jar : http://shallwedate.jp/en/bundle/bundle_002.html
